Package: limmahelpers
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions to Summarise and Visualise limma::lmFit Results
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eugene Slaughter
Maintainer: Eugene Slaughter <eugene.slaughter1994@gmail.com>
Description: limmahelpers is a personal R package containing helper functions
    to assist in the summarisation and visualisation of results from analyses
    conducted using the limma package in Bioconductor.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    broom,
    dplyr,
    DT,
    ggplot2,
    limma,
    plotly,
    tibble,
    tidyselect
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
